# Mac Mini Compose — Environment Variables
# Each stack has its own .env in its directory (core/.env, monitoring/.env).
# These are generated at deploy time by Komodo pre_deploy scripts via BWS.
# Secrets live in the existing k3s BWS project; the mac-mini machine account
# has read access and fetches each secret by UUID.
# NEVER commit .env files to git.
#
# === core/.env ===
# TECHNITIUM_ADMIN_PASSWORD=    # BWS: ae363b89-...
# MINI_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=       # BWS: a280e465-...
# MINI_POSTGRES_TODO_PASSWORD=  # BWS: 081051dc-...
# AGENT_KB_PASSWORD=            # BWS: 549c2404-...
# MONGO_PASSWORD=               # BWS: d0213758-...
# BACKUP_ACCESS_KEY=            # BWS: af4a292f-...
# BACKUP_SECRET_KEY=            # BWS: d2d87681-...
# BACKUP_ENDPOINT=              # BWS: 2c95ebd0-...
#
# === monitoring/.env ===
# TECHNITIUM_API_TOKEN=         # BWS: 4645ac46-...
# MINI_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=       # BWS: a280e465-...
# MONGO_PASSWORD=               # BWS: d0213758-...
#
# === monitoring/ha-token ===
# (plain text file — HA long-lived access token for Prometheus, BWS: c7ccdb87-...)
